name: Suspicious Lohikeitto
desc: A classic soup from the frigid regions. At first glance, it looks appetizing enough. However, a single sip reveals a burnt flavor that overwhelms your taste buds. You quickly inspect the pot and sure enough, the bottom is a charred, black mess... For the sake of your health, it's probably best to skip this one.

value.text: Restores 18% of Max HP to the selected character and regenerates 300 HP every 5s for 30s.
